We cannot deny the impact of the coronavirus pandemic on our livelihoods and this also includes how we look. How you wear and look can be affected by how you feel and we know that some are not coping at all mentally due to Covid-19. It is said wearing makeup can lift your mood and just because you are now always wearing a mask, it doesn't mean you should overlook it. For those who still need to be out there in these trying times, here is a little something that can help you lift your mood. Here's a video to help you with making your makeup last. 